'''王室屬地'''（{{lang-en|Crown Dependencies}}），或译作'''皇家属地'''{{NoteTag|1=中文译名参见[[新华社|新华社]]报道《[http://news.xinhuanet.com/energy/2017-09/21/c_1121698347.htm 马恩岛启动油气勘探招标]》、上海市人民政府外事办公室新闻通报《[http://www.shfao.gov.cn/wsb/node466/node467/node471/u1ai21357.html 英国皇家属地泽西岛政府首席部长代表团访沪]》、中国人民对外友好协会报道《[http://www.cpaffc.org.cn/content/details4-44078.html 谢元副会长宴请英国皇家属地泽西岛政府首席部长戈斯特]》、[[东网|东网]]新闻《[http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170517/bkn-20170517180137368-0517_00982_001.html 海峽群島大師旅程率先睇]》及[[中时电子报|中时电子报]]《[http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20131203000100-260203 比特幣夯 奧爾德尼島搶官方鑄造頭香]》等。}}、'''王權領地'''{{NoteTag|1=中文译名参见信报《[http://www2.hkej.com/commentary/finanalytics/article/1091055/從皇家海軍建軍模式看英國戰略轉變 從皇家海軍建軍模式看英國戰略轉變]》：「英國至今仍佈署超過3萬名軍人於海外（包含海外領地Overseas territories、王權領地Crown Dependencies與其他國家），與諸多國家維持軍事協議，近年來也確實全面性地參與各項國際事務，在第一時間投注人力、資源。」}}，是独立管理的司法管辖区，并非[[英国|大不列颠及北爱尔兰联合王国]]或[[英国海外领土|英国海外领土]]的一部分<ref>{{cite web|title=Crown Dependencies - Justice Committee|url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200910/cmselect/cmjust/56/5604.htm|accessdate=2016-11-14|date=2010-03-30|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68e5FeWIR?url=http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200910/cmselect/cmjust/56/5604.htm|archivedate=2012-06-23|dead-url=no|website=Parliament of the United Kingdom}}</ref>，而是[[官方_(法人)|英国王室]]的自治領地<ref name="Briefing2">{{cite web|title=Background briefing on the Crown dependencies: Jersey, Guernsey and the Isle of Man|url=http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/about/moj/our-responsibilities/Background_Briefing_on_the_Crown_Dependencies2.pdf|accessdate=2017-07-31|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191102104306/http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/about/moj/our-responsibilities/Background_Briefing_on_the_Crown_Dependencies2.pdf|archivedate=2019-11-02|dead-url=no|website=Ministry of Justice}}</ref>。而在国际上，英国皇家属地被认为是“[[英国|联合王国]]所负责的领土”，而不是[[主权国家|主权国家]]<ref name="International recognition">{{cite web|title=Fact sheet on the UK's relationship with the Crown Dependencies|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/361537/crown-dependencies.pdf|accessdate=2014-08-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209173145/https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/361537/crown-dependencies.pdf|archivedate=2014-12-09|dead-url=no|website=Ministry of Justice}}</ref>，简而言之其主权属于英国。因此，它们也不是[[英联邦|英联邦]]成员国<ref name="justice.gov.uk">{{cite web|title=Government Response to the Justice Select Committee's report: Crown Dependencies|url=http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/publications/moj/2010/gov-response-justice-select-committee-crowndependencies.pdf|accessdate=2017-07-21|date=2010-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108023424/http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/publications/moj/2010/gov-response-justice-select-committee-crowndependencies.pdf|archivedate=2017-11-08|dead-url=no|website=Ministry of Justice}}</ref>。但是，它们又的确与英联邦、[[欧洲联盟|欧盟]]及其他国际组织有關連，同时也是[[英国－爱尔兰理事会|英国－爱尔兰理事会]]的成员。皇家属地在[[英联邦运动会|英联邦运动会]]上拥有各自的代表队。在[[英国脱欧|英国脱欧]]之前，它们虽然不属于欧盟，但却在欧盟的{{Link-en|欧盟关税联盟|European Union Customs Union|关税区域}}内。由于皇家属地不是主权国家，因此影响这些地区的立法权最终由联合王国政府承担。但是，它们都拥有各自的立法机关，有权在王室（[[英國樞密院|枢密院]]，或者马恩岛在其{{Link-en|马恩岛总督|Lieutenant Governor of the Isle of Man|总督}}）许可下对地方事务进行立法<ref>{{cite web|title=Profile of Jersey|url=http://www.gov.je/ChiefMinister/International+Relations/Profile+of+Jersey.htm|accessdate=2008-07-31|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060902092534/http://www.gov.je/ChiefMinister/International%2BRelations/Profile%2Bof%2BJersey.htm|archivedate=2006-09-02|quote=The legislature passes primary legislation, which requires approval by The Queen in Council, and enacts subordinate legislation in many areas without any requirement for Royal Sanction and under powers conferred by primary legislation.|website=States of Jersey|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。而皇家属地各自的[[政府首脑|政府首脑]]均称为“[[首席部长|首席部长]]”（后根西行政区废除此职务改为委员会主席）。

== 名词定义 ==
{{Also|官方 (法人)}}

英国皇家属地对于“{{lang|en|The Crown}}”的定义各不相同。

在[[澤西|泽西岛]]，根据{{Link-en|王室法官|Law Officers of the Crown}}在21世纪宪法地位声明中所定义，“{{lang|en|The Crown}}”代表“泽西岛官方”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Review of the Roles of the Crown Officers|url=http://www5.gov.je/SiteCollectionDocuments/Government%20and%20administration/R%20Attorney%20General%20Transcript%2020100702%20WM.pdf|date=2010-07-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812153038/http://www5.gov.je/SiteCollectionDocuments/Government%20and%20administration/R%20Attorney%20General%20Transcript%2020100702%20WM.pdf|archivedate=2011-08-12|website=States of Jersey}}</ref>泽西岛行政区内所有官方辖地都属于泽西岛官方，而不是联合王国官方。<ref>{{cite web|title=Written Question To H.M. Attorney General by Deputy P.V.F. Le Claire of St. Helier|url=http://www.statesassembly.gov.je/documents/questions/23532-33785-2262010.htm|date=2010-06-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927015030/http://www.statesassembly.gov.je/documents/questions/23532-33785-2262010.htm|archivedate=2011-09-27|website=States of Jersey}}</ref>

[[曼島|马恩岛]]的立法机关也将“{{lang|en|The Crown}}”定义成“马恩岛官方”，而与“联合王国官方”以示区分。<ref>{{cite web|title=The Air Navigation (Isle of Man) Order 2007 (No. 1115)|url=http://www.statutelaw.gov.uk/content.aspx?LegType=All+Legislation&PageNumber=1&NavFrom=3&parentActiveTextDocId=3312343&ActiveTextDocId=3312364&filesize=13636|accessdate=2017-07-31|website=The National Archives|archive-date=2021-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328050859/https://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2007/1115/article/3/made|dead-url=no}}</ref>

而在[[根西|根西岛]]，立法机关将“{{lang|en|The Crown}}”定义成“行政区官方”。<ref>{{cite web|title=The Unregistered Design Rights (Bailiwick of Guernsey) Ordinance|url=http://www.guernseylegalresources.gg/ccm/legal-resources/ordinances/intellectual-property/unregistered-design-rights-bailiwick-of-guernsey-ordinance-2005.en|year=2005|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721031210/http://www.guernseylegalresources.gg/ccm/legal-resources/ordinances/intellectual-property/unregistered-design-rights-bailiwick-of-guernsey-ordinance-2005.en|archivedate=2011-07-21|website=Guernsey Legal Resources}}</ref>根西岛王室法官则提出“在文本上，‘{{lang|en|The Crown}}’通常指根西岛行政区全体。”<ref name="RJCO2010">{{cite web|title=Review of the Roles of the Jersey Crown officers|url=http://www.gov.je/SiteCollectionDocuments/Government%20and%20administration/R%20Guernsey%20LOs%20Submission%2020100330%20HR%20v1.pdf|accessdate=2017-07-31|date=2012-03-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010220559/https://www.gov.je/SiteCollectionDocuments/Government%20and%20administration/R%20Guernsey%20LOs%20Submission%2020100330%20HR%20v1.pdf|archivedate=2017-10-10|dead-url=no|website=States of Jersey}}</ref>而且这包括“在君主建立下或由君主授权下建立的用于管理这些岛屿的政府机关或民间机构，这包含根西岛及其他岛屿的立法机关，皇家法院和其他法院，副总督、教区当局，以及在枢密院内和通过枢密院授权行事的组织或个人。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thisisguernsey.com/2010/06/21/its-a-power-thing/|title=It's a power thing…|date=2010-06-21|first=Joel|last=de Woolfson|newspaper=Guernsey Press|accessdate=2017-07-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610140928/http://www.thisisguernsey.com/2010/06/21/its-a-power-thing/|archivedate=2011-06-30}}</ref>这一宪法概念也被称为“根西岛行政区官方”。<ref name="RJCO2010" />

